
ðŸ”¹ Product-Level Aggregations
1. Product Monthly Sales
{ FIXED [Product], DATETRUNC('month',[Order_Date]) :
    SUM([Total_Sales])
}

2. Product Total Sales
{ FIXED [Product] :
    SUM([Total_Sales])
}

ðŸ”¹ Category & Brand Metrics
3. Category Total Sales
{ FIXED [Category] :
    SUM([Total_Sales])
}

4. Brand Total Sales
{ FIXED [Brand] :
    SUM([Total_Sales])
}

ðŸ”¹ Customer-Level Metrics
5. Customer Lifetime Sales
{ FIXED [Customer_Name] :
    SUM([Total_Sales])
}

6. Orders per Customer
{ FIXED [Customer_Name] :
    COUNTD([Order_Number])
}

ðŸ”¹ Margin Risk Counts
7. Low Margin Product Count
{ FIXED [Product] :
    IF SUM([Total_Sales]) - SUM([Total_Cost]) < 0.10 * SUM([Total_Sales])
    THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
}
